## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This Zero Trust project demonstrates secure network segmentation, certificate-based authentication, device compliance scoring, monitoring and detection using SIEM, anomaly detection using ML, automated quarantine response, and full testing documentation.

This wiki contains:
- Step-by-step implementation
- Scripts & configs
